B2%BD-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"2 가상 환경 생성 스크립트 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2. 가상 환경 생성 스크립트</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">create_venv.bat</code> 파일 생성:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"batch\"><pre class=\"language-batch\"><code class=\"language-batch\"><span class=\"token operator\">@</span><span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> off</span>\n<span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> <span class=\"token parameter attr-name\">-m</span> venv venv</span>\n<span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">call</span> venv\\Scripts\\activate.bat</span>\n<span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> <span class=\"token parameter attr-name\">-m</span> pip install <span class=\"token parameter attr-name\">--upgrade</span> pip</span>\n<span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">pip</span> install <span class=\"token parameter attr-name\">-r</span> requirements.txt</span>\n<span class=\"token command\"><span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> Virtual environment setup complete!</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-자동-활성화-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 자동 활성화 설정 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>3. 자동 활성화 설정</h3>\n<p>PowerShell 프로필에 다음 함수 추가:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># $PROFILE 파일에 추가</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> activate-venv <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">Test-Path</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"venv\\Scripts\\activate.ps1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\venv\\Scripts\\activate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ps1\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">Write-Host</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No venv found in current directory\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"보안-고려사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B3%B4%EC%95%88-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A0%A4%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"보안 고려사항 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>보안 고려사항</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>실행 정책을 변경할 때는 보안 위험을 고려하세요.</li>\n<li>가능하면 <code class=\"language-text\">RemoteSigned</code>를 사용하고, <code class=\"language-text\">Unrestricted</code>는 피하세요.</li>\n<li>사용자 범위(<code class=\"language-text\">-Scope CurrentUser</code>)로 제한하는 것이 좋습니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"추가-팁\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80-%ED%8C%81\" aria-label=\"추가 팁 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>추가 팁</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>가상 환경 이름 표시 확인</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 활성화 성공 시 프롬프트 앞에 (venv)가 표시됨</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>venv<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">PS</span> C:\\your-project></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Python 버전 확인</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">python <span class=\"token operator\">--</span>version\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 가상 환경의 Python 버전이 맞는지 확인</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>의존성 관리</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 설치된 패키지 목록 저장</span>\npip freeze > requirements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>txt\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 패키지 설치</span>\npip install <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>r requirements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>txt</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>문제가 지속되면 Python을 완전히 제거하고 재설치하는 것도 고려해볼 수 있습니다.</p>","fro